{
  "texts": [
    "Taken together, these data confirmed that DEEPOMICS FFPE can effectively discriminate between FFPE-artifacts and true variants.",
    "FFPE allows the archival of clinical samples at room temperature for several decades without compromising histomorphology.",
    "However, FFPE specimens contain artifactual mutations.",
    "Thus, removal of such artifact is important to improve variant calling for precision medicine.",
    "DEEPOMICS FFPE is effective in removing FFPE artifacts, although some true variants were inadvertently filtered out."
  ]
}